Class Solver

  • java.lang.Object
    • Solver

  • public class Solver
extends java.lang.Object
    Given a itinerary and the obstacles between the start and the end of the itinerary. The objective is to count the number of obstacles that intersect the itinerary. The solver is used to solve the specific problem, we receive some geometric figures and a line segment, we count the number of given figures that intersect the line segment.
    Since:
    04/11/2016
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
